               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     3ra-181rc)
 I-1) Maggābit (fols. 3ra-35vb)
 I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     36ra-60va)
 I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 61ra-93rb) 
 I-4) Sane (fols.
                     94ra-122vc)
 I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 123ra-155ra)
 I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     156ra-176rb)
 I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 177ra-181ra) 
 - Postscript
                     (commissioner's statement): fol. 181ra
 - Za-ʾaqrabku māḥleta... “The song
                     I am offering...” (concluding prayer): fol. 181ra-rb
 The commemorative
                     notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
